{
  "id": "615ebe8cfff5a8001d738bd8",
  "title": "Scrapboxでマンダラート",
  "created": 1633599118,
  "updated": 1650767103,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "615ebe8cfff5a8001d738bd8",
      "text": "Scrapboxでマンダラート",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599118,
      "updated": 1633599118
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebe8e5b98c20000b07b9e",
      "text": " table:mandal-art-01",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599118,
      "updated": 1633599137
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebea15b98c20000b07b9f",
      "text": " \t[創造性]\t[マンダラート]\t[知的生産]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599137,
      "updated": 1633599137
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebea15b98c20000b07ba0",
      "text": " \t[テーブル記法]\t[Scrapbox.icon]\t[リンク記法]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599137,
      "updated": 1633599137
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebea15b98c20000b07ba1",
      "text": " \t[情報共有]\t[井戸端.icon]\t[課題解決]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599137,
      "updated": 1633599152
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebea15b98c20000b07ba2",
      "text": "　正確には、「[マンダラート]っぽい使い方」いうべきかもしれない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599137,
      "updated": 1633599468
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebebc5b98c20000b07ba4",
      "text": "　 Scrapboxで、[テーブル記法]内に[リンク記法]と[アイコン記法]が使えるようになった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599165,
      "updated": 1633599486
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07ba9",
      "text": "  簡易的なマンダラートが実現できる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599236
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07baa",
      "text": " Scrapboxでマンダラートの進め方",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599240
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bab",
      "text": "  マンダラート用のページをつくる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599247
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bac",
      "text": "   課題をページタイトルにする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599254
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bad",
      "text": "  テーブル記法で3x3のマトリックスをつくる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599259
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bae",
      "text": "  真ん中に課題（ページタイトル）を書き入れる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599264
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07baf",
      "text": "  残り8つのマスに解決策を書き入れる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599269
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bb0",
      "text": "  解決策をリンク記法（またはアイコン記法）にする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599275
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bb1",
      "text": "  （オプション）ページの余白に、補足情報を書く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599280
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bb2",
      "text": "  8つのマスのページについても同様に3x3のマトリックスをつくりマスを埋める",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599289
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bb3",
      "text": "   ページがなければ作る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599297
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bb4",
      "text": "   9x9の81項目ができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599304
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bb5",
      "text": "  （オプション）細分化できなくなるまで繰り返し",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599310
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bb6",
      "text": " マンダラート用テンプレート",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599315
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebef75b98c20000b07bb7",
      "text": "  table:mandal-art",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599223,
      "updated": 1633599406
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf745b98c20000b07bb8",
      "text": "  \t1\t2\t3",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599348,
      "updated": 1633599406
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf745b98c20000b07bb9",
      "text": "  \t4\t5\t6",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599348,
      "updated": 1633599406
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf745b98c20000b07bba",
      "text": "  \t7\t8\t9",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599348,
      "updated": 1633599406
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf9b5b98c20000b07bc3",
      "text": " やってみた感想[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599388,
      "updated": 1633600146
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf9c5b98c20000b07bc4",
      "text": "  3x3のマトリックスにする意味がわからない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599388,
      "updated": 1633599411
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf9c5b98c20000b07bc5",
      "text": "   箇条書きのほうが簡単、柔軟",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599388,
      "updated": 1633599418
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec33179e1130000b98c6a",
      "text": "   自由に思考していると深ぼらないような事を強制的に考えさせてくるのが良さだと思っている[blu3mo.icon][基素.icon]",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1633600305,
      "updated": 1646747118
    },
    {
      "id": "6180076232ef920000eeb867",
      "text": "   \tなるほどなぁ[dokudami.icon]",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1635780450,
      "updated": 1635780453
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec37079e1130000b98c6b",
      "text": "   （何か書くとそれについて8個ネタを出さざるを得ないので、頭を絞れる）",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1633600369,
      "updated": 1633600393
    },
    {
      "id": "61a26a0faff09e000036f311",
      "text": "   [枠があると埋めたくな]る気持ちを利用する色々なフレームワークの一種でマスが8つあるだけのフレームワークなのだという認識[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1638033935,
      "updated": 1638095318
    },
    {
      "id": "61a26a48aff09e000036f312",
      "text": "    ところで「枠があると埋めたくなる、全部埋めるとスッキリしてハッピーになる」って性格とScrapboxに自由に書きたい系の性格ってもしかして相反するのかな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1638033993,
      "updated": 1638034088
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf9c5b98c20000b07bc6",
      "text": "  [ブレインストーミング]・[強制連想法]のバリエーションだね、こりゃ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599388,
      "updated": 1633600645
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf9c5b98c20000b07bc7",
      "text": " 今後の課題",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599388,
      "updated": 1633599429
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf9c5b98c20000b07bc8",
      "text": "  テーブル（表）を見やすくする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599388,
      "updated": 1633599433
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf9c5b98c20000b07bc9",
      "text": "  関連ページリストでのプレビューをいい感じにする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599388,
      "updated": 1633599438
    },
    {
      "id": "615ebf9c5b98c20000b07bca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1633599388,
      "updated": 1633599388
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec32aa336820000cfb231",
      "text": "`name.icon`",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600299,
      "updated": 1633600318
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec33fa336820000cfb233",
      "text": "\t1",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600320,
      "updated": 1633600321
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec34aa336820000cfb238",
      "text": "\t\t1-1",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600330,
      "updated": 1633600332
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec34da336820000cfb239",
      "text": "\t\t1-2",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600333,
      "updated": 1633600335
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec34fa336820000cfb23a",
      "text": "\t\t..",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600336,
      "updated": 1633600338
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec352a336820000cfb23b",
      "text": "\t\t1-9",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600338,
      "updated": 1633600410
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec341a336820000cfb234",
      "text": "\t2",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600321,
      "updated": 1633600323
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec342a336820000cfb235",
      "text": "\t..",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600323,
      "updated": 1633600326
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec346a336820000cfb237",
      "text": "\t8",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600327,
      "updated": 1633600425
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec32fa336820000cfb232",
      "text": "とかにすればそれは実質的なマンダラート?[erniogi.icon]",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600304,
      "updated": 1633600368
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec376a336820000cfb23e",
      "text": "\tマンダラートはたぶん立体で作ったほうが面白そう[erniogi.icon]",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600375,
      "updated": 1633600402
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec370a336820000cfb23d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600368,
      "updated": 1633600368
    },
    {
      "id": "615f7f738ee92a00000c5a74",
      "text": "マンダラートみたいに使えるものが欲しいと思ってScrapboxを作ったという経緯はあります [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1633648499,
      "updated": 1633648551
    },
    {
      "id": "615ec35ca336820000cfb23c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1633600349,
      "updated": 1633600349
    },
    {
      "id": "61a2b9e279d3a90000fe92c3",
      "text": "箇条書きだと一次元だが、マンダラートだと二次元にできるので空間的制約の無さという意味で自由に発想しやすそう[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1638054371,
      "updated": 1638098339
    },
    {
      "id": "61a2b9dc79d3a90000fe92c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1638054366,
      "updated": 1638095329
    },
    {
      "id": "61a359dc1280f00000540f34",
      "text": "[/unnamedcamp/マンダラート自作]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1638095325,
      "updated": 1650720103
    },
    {
      "id": "6263fd675b98c20000c3b1eb",
      "text": "[/sta/Scrapbox上でマンダラートを自作する]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1650720103,
      "updated": 1650720145
    },
    {
      "id": "6264b4ec79d3a90000df74ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1650767086,
      "updated": 1650767086
    },
    {
      "id": "6264b4ec79d3a90000df74af",
      "text": "table記法で頑張るマン",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1650767086,
      "updated": 1650767092
    },
    {
      "id": "6264b4f379d3a90000df74b2",
      "text": "\t[/sta/マンダラートテンプレート MandalArt Template]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1650767094,
      "updated": 1650767094
    },
    {
      "id": "6264b4f479d3a90000df74b3",
      "text": "\tどんどん右側にずれていくｗ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1650767094,
      "updated": 1650767103
    },
